Explanation:

main.dart: Entry point of your Flutter app.

src: Short for "source code," this directory contains your main application code.

pages: Contains individual pages/screens of your app.

home_page.dart: Your app's home page.
sign_in_page.dart: Page for mobile phone OTP authentication.
widgets: Reusable UI components.

custom_button.dart: A button with custom styling.
otp_input_field.dart: Widget for OTP input field.
Other widgets you may need.
services: Business logic and services.

authentication_service.dart: Handles user authentication logic.
models: Data models for your app.

user.dart: Represents the user model.
utils: Utility functions or constants.

constants.dart: App-wide constants.
validators.dart: Functions for input validation.